{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 200022,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ま、まあいいや……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"W-well, I guess it's fine...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200023,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　いや、まったく良くはないけど」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "No, it's not fine at all, though.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200024,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ガーン！？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Gah!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200025,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「もーっ、なんでお前は",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Geez, why do you always"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200026,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そんなことばっかり言うんだよー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "say things like that all the time!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200027,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ぺちぺちぺちぺちぺち。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "*pat pat pat pat pat.*"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200028,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あなたは足を長田君に叩かれまくった。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You were repeatedly hit on your legs by Nagata-kun."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200029,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「へんっ、だ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmph!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200030,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「＜エール＞には俺がついてないと心配だからな！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I'm worried if I'm not with Eiru!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200031,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　一緒に行ってやるさ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I'll go along with you!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200032,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そう、相棒としてなー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That's right, as your partner!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200033,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なに言ってるんだか……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"What are you talking about...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200034,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「まあ、いいじゃないか。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, isn't it fine?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200035,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　やっぱり僕らのパーティーには彼がいないとね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "After all, our party wouldn't be complete without him.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200036,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うっし！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Alright!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200037,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　とにかくこれで全員で行くことが決定したな！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Anyway, it's decided that we'll all go together now!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200038,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ああ、今度こそ――」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yeah, this time for sure—\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200039,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ま――」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Wai—\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200040,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「待ってーーーー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Wait——!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200041,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "キーンとリアの声が室内に響いた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Ria's high-pitched voice echoed through the room."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200042,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うるせぇよ、母さん。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Shut up, Mom."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200043,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そんな声出さなくても聞こえるよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I can hear you even if you don't shout like that.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200044,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「駄目駄目駄目駄目駄目ー！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No no no no no—!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200045,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　翔竜山に行くのは絶対駄目ー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Going to Mount Shoryu is absolutely forbidden!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200046,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「アア？　あんでだよ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh? Why's that?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200047,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なんでって決まってるでしょ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Why? It's obvious..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200048,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　自分の子供を死地に送りたい親がどこにいるの」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "What parent would want to send their own child into a deadly place?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200049,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「で、でもママ――」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"B-but Mom—\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200050,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "スシヌの言葉をマジックが手で制して遮る。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Magic stopped Sushinu's words with a hand gesture."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200051,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「確かに一度は行けと命じたし……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It's true I ordered you to go once..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200052,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それは今更翻すのがどういうことか分かってる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I understand what it means to reverse that now.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200053,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それが間違ってるのも分かるけど……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I also know that it was wrong, but..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200054,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「でも……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"But..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200055,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　自分の子供が死ぬかもしれないのに、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Even though your own child might die,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200056,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　それを応援なんて出来るわけないじゃない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "there's no way you can cheer for that.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200057,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ま、ママ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"M-mom...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200058,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ごめんね……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I'm sorry..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200059,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　あなた達がそれだけ言ってくれたのに、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Even though you said so much to me,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200060,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　母さんの方が先に折れちゃって……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Mom was the one who gave in first...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200061,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「妾も反対じゃ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I am against it as well.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200062,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「お母さんまで……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even Mom...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200063,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「というか！　妾はずーーーっと反対しておるわ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Or rather! I've been against it the whole time!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200064,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ね？　ね？　ね？",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Right? Right? Right?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200065,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ダーリンとはもう戦わなくていいから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "You don't have to fight, darling,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200066,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もうJAPANに引っ込んで遊んで暮らそう？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "so why don't you just retire to JAPAN and live a carefree life?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200067,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ダーリンだってもしかしたら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Even darling might not,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200068,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔王には覚醒しないかも知れないし、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "awaken as the Demon King,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200069,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　覚醒しても支配なんて考えないかも……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "or even if he does awaken, might not intend to dominate...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200070,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いや、行く」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"No, I'm going.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200071,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「悪いな、母さん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Sorry, Mom.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200072,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「う、う、うううう……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"U-uuu...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200073,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「やーーーーー！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Nooooo!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200074,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　やだーーーーーーーー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I don't want toooooo!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200075,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「やだーって……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"'I don't want to'... You're no longer a child..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200076,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　んな子供じゃあるめぇし……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200077,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「途中で倒れて魔人にアメージング城まで",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"When I heard you collapsed halfway and were taken to Amazing Castle by demons,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200078,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　さらわれたって聞いた時、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200079,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　リアがどんな気持ちでいたと思ってるの！？\"",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "do you know how Ria felt!?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200080,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「その上、クエルプランまで",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"And on top of that, when I heard that the Quelplan was initiated..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 200081,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　発生したと聞いた時は…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    }
  ]
}

